<h1>This is the archive</h1>

<h2>It is static HTML generated out of Ode with the help of a simple Bash script that uses the <a href="http://curl.haxx.se/">curl</a> and <a href="http://www.cis.upenn.edu/~bcpierce/unison/">Unison</a> utilities. You can also visit <a href="/blog">the blog home</a>. </h2>

